        "content": "<h3>Difficulty</h3>\n\n<p>Hard</p>\n\n<h3>Importance</h3>\n\n<p>★★★★★</p>\n\n<h3>Frequency</h3>\n\n<p>★★★★☆</p>\n\n<hr>"
