        "content": "<p>RoCE performs best when packet loss is minimized.</p>\n\n<p>Technologies often used:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>PFC</li>\n<li>ECN</li>\n<li>DCB</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>"
