        "title": "Real Kubernetes Example",
        "content": "<p>Request 1: <br> 요청 1:<br><pre><code class=\"language-text\">https://api.company.com/users</code></pre><br>↓<br>Ingress (L7 Load Balancer)<br>↓<br>Service A (User Service)</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Request 2: <br> 요청 2:<br><pre><code class=\"language-text\">https://api.company.com/orders</code></pre><br>↓<br>Ingress (L7 Load Balancer)<br>↓<br>Service B (Order Service)</p>\n\n<p>This is L7 routing. <br> 이것이 전형적인 경로 기준(Path-based) L7 라우팅의 동작 흐름입니다.</p>\n\n<hr>"
