        "title": "8. ss",
        "content": "<h3>Purpose<br>목적</h3>\n\n<p>Network connection analysis.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Common Command</h3>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">ss -tulpn</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Why Use It?</h3>\n\n<p>Inspect:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Open ports</li>\n<li>Connections</li>\n<li>Listening services</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Modern Replacement</h3>\n\n<p>Preferred over netstat.</p>\n\n<hr>"
